---
title: Eggs-In-A-Hole Skillet with Chickpeas and Swiss Chard
description: Eggs may be a breakfast mainstay, but as far as we’re concerned, they’re good to eat at any time of day. Especially when you pair them with hearty veggies and a tomato-y sauce, they instantly become a meal worthy of your dinner plate. Here, you’ve got tender Swiss chard and chickpeas to spare—just the thing to fortify you at the end of a long day.
